08/27/80	message.compin

Syntax:  .ifi message	"message" "alternate message" ...
      OR .ifi msg		"message" "alternate message" ...


Function:
This macro places an interactive subsystem (eg, qedx, read_mail, or
ol_dump) message on the page.


Macro action:
1) inserts message separation white space as appropriate for the device
2) formats "message" and any number of "alternate message"'s in 9pt
   ascii, each on a line by itself,  hanging by one indentation level

(END)
